article_id:2384,category_name:News,title_name:Regarding a Network Connection Issue [Update],image_path:,message:<div><span style="color: rgb(41, 105, 176);"><strong>[Addendum <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1627372800"></span>]</strong></span><br>Players who had purchased the 7-Day Pack (Double Bonus) did not receive the extra amount of items they should have obtained.<br><br>We will send these items to all affected players starting <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1627372800"></span>.<br><br>Thank you for your patience.</div><div><br></div><hr><div><span style="color: rgb(41, 105, 176);"><strong>[Addendum <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1627297200"></span>]</strong></span><br>In relation to this issue, the following issues occurred between approximately <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1627281000"></span> and <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1627281300"></span>.<br><br>■Details of the issues<br>・When playing any quest besides the Trials of the Mighty quests that provide a daily bonus, an error occurred which made it impossible to clear the quest.<br>・The daily bonus for Trials of the Mighty quests could not be obtained even when clearing these quests.<br><br>These issues have now been resolved.<br><br>We have also sent all players who cleared Trials of the Mighty quests while these issues were occurring the daily bonus items that they should have received when clearing said quests.<br>These items can be claimed from your goodie box.</div><div><br></div><hr><div>We have confirmed that a network issue was temporarily preventing connection to the Dragalia Lost game around <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1627281000"></span>.&nbsp;</div><div>This issue has now been resolved.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1627282200,update_time1627372786